Anonymous Sun 27 Oct 2024 14:20:46 No.70329453 Report
Quoted By: >>70329500
>>70329397
You're probably running both 4ChanX and 4ChanXT at once. The proper procedure is:
1) Export 4ChanX config
2) Disable 4ChanX
3) Install 4ChanXT
4) Import 4ChanX configuration to 4ChanXT

You can't run both at the same time and they don't share the same config.
